Author: QUASA
Title: [BOUNTY] QUASA OPEN LOGISTICS BLOCKCHAIN PLATFORM
Body: QUASA offers a new model of cargo transportation with a simple interface for end users and allows you to make orders on the most favorable terms in just a couple of clicks. The company organizes cargo transportation, bypassing intermediaries. Thanks to the developed IT solution, QUASA distributes orders in such a way that carriers can make the most efficient use of transport. This optimization allows simultaneously to increase the efficiency of cargo carriers, thereby increasing their revenue, and at the same time to reduce the cost of transportation for cargo owners.  However, first of all, QUASA is unique in its economic system based on QuasaCoins' own crypto currency, which is designed to protect cargo owners and cargo carriers, and offers innovative solutions based on the implementation of blockchain technology in supply chain management

Author: QUASA1
Title: [BOUNTY] QUASA OPEN LOGISTICS BLOCKCHAIN PLATFORM
Body: Once the ICO is completed, the QUASA tokens will be listed on several exchanges to provide investors with liquidity. The basic currency of QUASA first rounds of ICO is ETH. During the secret round, the cost of the QUASA token is 0.0001 ETH, during preIO QUASA the price is 0.00016 ETH, and during the ICO round, the cost of QuasaCoins is 0.00033 ETH Therefore, early birds receive a significant bonus.

Author: QUASA1
Title: [BOUNTY] QUASA OPEN LOGISTICS BLOCKCHAIN PLATFORM
Body: In the closed round QUASA team offers investors 9,25 million tokens QuasaCoins in the ammount of 925 ETH The price for 1 token QUASA in the preICO round will be twice higher than on the first round. In the ICO round the price goes double again. For those who participates in the closed round the price after ICO will grow 4 times After ICO QUASA team increases the price 5 times from the current QUA price and will cost 2000 QUA for 1 ETH.

Author: QUASA1
Title: [BOUNTY] QUASA OPEN LOGISTICS BLOCKCHAIN PLATFORM
Body: Friends, For the first investors, for you, the best conditions! Only now we sell our currency, QuasaCoin (QUA), with a discount of 80% and more such an offer will never be. Thank you!

Author: QUASA1
Title: [BOUNTY] QUASA OPEN LOGISTICS BLOCKCHAIN PLATFORM
Body: YOUR BENEFIT IS IN DIRECT CORRELATION WITH THE STAGE ON WHICH YOU JOIN QUASA.  In other words, at preICO which will take place on January 15 we are going to sell our QUA at an almost double price, comparing to this round. This means that your benefit from the purchased QUA doubles almost immediately.  At ICO on February 15 the price of QUA will be doubled again. For those who join us now, the post-ICO price will grow 4 times.  In March we are going to make the price of QUA five times higher comparing to its current level. Hence, we will be selling 2,000 QUA for 1 ETH and will fix this rate on our website. That is, those who would like to get QUA later will be able to buy not more than 2,000 QUA for 1 ETH.

Title: [BOUNTY] QUASA OPEN LOGISTICS BLOCKCHAIN PLATFORM

Author: QUASA
Title: [BOUNTY] QUASA OPEN LOGISTICS BLOCKCHAIN PLATFORM
Body: To avoid future damages, QUA will be frozen in your wallets till 30 March 2018. This will be done so that people do not rush to the exchange all together and do not crush the QUA rate. We understand that afterwards the QUA rate will stabilize and grow but still we would prefer to avoid this.  Bonus. Tokens sold out at preICO will be defrost 30 May for tokens realized at ICO this will take place – 30 June. Hence, you will be the first and the only market participants who will be able to trade in QUA on exclusive terms.

During the secret round, the cost of the QUASA token is 0.0001 ETH, during preIO QUASA the price is 0.00016 ETH, and during the ICO round, the cost of QuasaCoins is 0.00033 ETH Therefore, early birds receive a significant bonus.

New technologies can significantly reduce the lack of trust, information barriers and legal costs.

Title: [BOUNTY] QUASA OPEN LOGISTICS BLOCKCHAIN PLATFORM
Body: Payment algorithm  The use of an external payment system helps:  not to elaborate own payment system and not to assume additional development risks; not to use QUASA platform as intermediary for performing transactions. The first stage includes the use of RIPPLEAPI protocol as payment system. During the selection of a payment system protocol, QUASA focused on open solutions with the following features: a) availability of a tested and developed infrastructure (industrial mode); b) open source code; c) high degree of trust of the community towards consensus protocols and decentralized network of independent centers.

Author: QUASA
Title: [BOUNTY] QUASA OPEN LOGISTICS BLOCKCHAIN PLATFORM
Body: Logistics is not only about moving a cargo. It also involves the movement of big volumes of information about shippers and receivers, the nature of the cargo, how to handle and pack it, what should be done with this cargo in the final place of destination, etc. It goes without saying that logistics deals with huge paperwork which makes this complicated industry even more opaque. The end receiver is not able to track the path that had been made by the cargo before it reached the receiver.

Body: QUASA announced the imminent beginning of the secret round of ICO. In a secret round, the QUASA team will offer investors 9.25 million QUASA tokens for a total of 925 ETH. The price of 1 QUASA token during the preICO round will be yes times higher than at the first. At ICO, the price will double again. For those who will enter now, the price after ICO grows 4 times. After ICO, the QUASA team will raise the price 5 times from the QUA price of the current stage, and it will cost 2000 QUA for one ETH and this will be fixed on the site. That is, those who want to get a QUA later, will be able to buy no more than 2000 QUA for 1 ETH. Once the ICO is completed, the QUASA tokens will be listed on several exchanges to provide investors with liquidity. The basic currency of QUASA first rounds of ICO is ETH. During the secret round, the cost of the QUASA token is 0.0001 ETH, during preICO QUASA the price is 0.00016 ETH, and during the ICO round, the cost of QuasaCoins is 0.00033 ETH Therefore, early birds receive a significant bonus.

Author: QUASA
Title: [BOUNTY] QUASA OPEN LOGISTICS BLOCKCHAIN PLATFORM
Body: Backstory  A long path had been traveled before the BLOCKCHAIN logistic solution has been invented. First of all, major carriers integrated the tariffs into their ERP systems in order to be able to give quicker responses to delivery requests. Later on they went online while smaller carriers started using forums and information panels for advertizing their services. Finally, UBER-like cargo services appeared. They typically offer truck transportation, so multimodal delivery is not available yet. All in all, centralized platforms cannot manage up-to-date and competitive prices or algorithms which exclude cargo damages, but new technologies could change this state of affairs.  The business strategy of the multimodal application is based on providing customers with absolutely new way of interacting with the logistics market.

QUASA is a platform that connects cargo owners and cargo carriers  Decentralized logistics platform QUASA offers innovative solutions based on the blockchain technology implementation into supply chains management The functionality of the system is created to protect cargo carriers and cargo owners. Title: [BOUNTY] QUASA OPEN LOGISTICS BLOCKCHAIN PLATFORM
Body: QUASA.NET is a platform for calculating prices and ordering freight. On the project platform, the user inputs the cargo departure and destination points, indicates its dimensions and weight, after that the system provides information on possible delivery options, the cost of each of them and the time. The client himself can choose the most suitable mode of transport, a particular carrier and place an order. Thus, users save on the commission fee, which in such transactions is paid to the company-expeditor. The order is processed through the electronic document management system and does not require paperwork.

Body: LISTING    ICOBENCH ICOHOLDER COINHILLS ICOLAND ICOHOTLIST ICOBUFFER TRACKICO COINJINJA STARTUPRANKING         CRYPTONEXT ICOSIREN BETICO CRYPTOCOMPARE ICOBAZAAR FINDICO INVESTFUTURE ICOBULL ICOPLUM TRULYCOIN CRUNCHBASE AGGREGATORICO THETOKENER ICOTOP  Prototype #Blockchain Platform: https://www.quasa.net/en  White Paper: http://www.quasa.io/whitePaper GitHub: https://github.com/quasagroup/contracts Etherscan: https://etherscan.io/token/0x4dAeb4a06F70f4b1A5C329115731fE4b89C0B227  Budget allocation: Campaign on Facebook: 20% Twitter Campaign: 20% Translation and moderation: 20% Media campaign: 16 440 QUA - Completed! Kickico Campaign: 4 175 QUA - Completed! Youtube Campaign: 24 175 QUA - Completed! Telegram: 24 175 QUA - Completed!  QUASA is an open IT system that uses a blockchain and consists of several smart contracts within the process of supply chain logistics. The system transfers the process of goods movement between cargo owners and cargo carriers to a new level of technical solutions, and ensures complete safety and confidentiality throughout the supply chain.  QUASA platform is a system product of a consortium of logistics and IT companies. www.quasa.io    QUASA Kickico Campaign QUASA won the rating of projects Kickico! Thank you for your participation, the campaign is closed!  Each of the campaign participants received 100 QUA on their wallet.  Statistics of participants:->here    QUASA Twitter Campaign 483 500 QUA of the bounty pool to be allocated to the Twitter campaign.  Terms: · Each member of Twitter Bounty campaign should have at least 100 followers · Then, each member should follow official QUASA page https://twitter.com/quasagroup and retweet at least one QUASA tweet per week. · The bounty campaign timing is till the end of ICO. In order to receive the bonus, each member is expected to participate till the end of the campaign. · A member, who has not retweeted tweets during one week or unfollowed QUASA official page, is not eligible for a reward. The list of participants is being updated and analyzed once per week. Each accepted campaign member is to receive 1 share per week. After ICO is finished, the whole QUASA bounty pool is to be redistributed among all campaign members considering the number of shares each member has. All members are to receive the reward to their wallets.  Participate: Attention! Fill in the table on a weekly basis. 7 WEEK -  8 WEEK - Closed Open  9 - 10 WEEKS - https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfKg3oH3YUnUHULtv9YvoBwXx8ShJEuBQ42gdB6Rq1OoFxUGw/viewform Thank you for your participation. You can monitor statistics ->here    QUASA Facebook Campaign 483 500 QUA of the bounty pool to be allocated to the Facebook campaign.  Terms: · Each member of Facebook Bounty campaign should have at least 300 friends · In order to participate, each member should go through registration · Then, each member should follow official QUASA page FACEBOOK LINK https://www.facebook.com/quasagroup, like and follow the QUASA page, and re-post at least one QUASA post per week. · The bounty campaign timing is until the end of ICO. In order to receive the bonus, each member is expected to participate until the end of the campaign. · A member, who has not hit Like, or has not shared posts during one week, or unfollowed QUASA official page is not eligible for a reward. The list of participants is being updated and analyzed once per week. Each accepted campaign member is to receive 1 share per week. After ICO is finished, the whole QUASA bounty pool is to be redistributed among all campaign members considering the number of shares each member has. All members are to receive the reward to their wallets.  Participate: Attention! Fill in the table on a weekly basis. 7 WEEK -  8 WEEK - Closed Open 9 - 10 WEEKS - https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSd32WldETXHWE5MDQEhLpcTi8Fo28W6BWmS_G6219tC-GYO5A/viewform Thank you for your participation. Stage: · Each of the campaign participants received 10 QUA on their wallet   Statistics of participants ->here    QUASA Translation and Moderation Campaign 483 500 QUA of the bounty pool to be allocated to the bitcointalk translation and moderation. Translator have to moderate too the local thread page for all the pre-sale and token sale period. Please reserve your language writing on the Bounty ANN thread of QUASA.  Rules for translations: 1. No google translator threads will be accepted. Must be good quality 2. You must also moderate your thread 3. Users that do not moderate their thread will receive 0 compensation 4. Users will be responsible for updating their threads with latest news from QUASA 5. News, updates and content needing translation can be found in the ANN thread (coming soon) Rewards: Each qualifying translation will earn 9500 QUA  Participate: Registration is open ->QUASA FORM Thank you for your participation.
